WEBVTT

00:03.376 --> 00:05.938
We've got to ring the police.
We're going to go to the police

00:05.939 --> 00:06.942
after we've got her back.

00:06.943 --> 00:08.870
Well, it's not mine.

00:08.871 --> 00:09.890
Hands behind your back.

00:09.891 --> 00:11.910
I'm not your mother.
Nobody bullies you.

00:11.911 --> 00:13.850
You're a police officer.

00:13.851 --> 00:14.894
I did this stupid thing.

00:14.895 --> 00:16.563
You never finished telling me
your story.

00:16.580 --> 00:17.651
It wasn't... really a police matter.

00:17.652 --> 00:20.615
Why have I just had police
knocking on door?

00:20.616 --> 00:22.619
Just get her ready to shift her.

00:22.620 --> 00:24.623
Where are we taking her?
I don't know yet.

00:24.624 --> 00:26.608
Just ring me
as soon as you're on the move.

00:26.710 --> 00:28.685
Becky, my daughter...

00:28.686 --> 00:30.757
died just after Ryan was born.

00:30.758 --> 00:32.680
She was raped.

00:32.682 --> 00:34.673
Is that what you're going to
do - mark his card for him?

00:34.674 --> 00:36.710
My intention is to deal with it
effectively.

