00:49.865 --> 00:50.901
You are kidding me?!

00:52.011 --> 00:53.449
'I'm not.'

00:53.450 --> 00:55.453
You're lying.
'Nope.'

00:55.454 --> 00:57.497
That's disgusting!

00:57.498 --> 00:59.481
They don't call it animal husbandry
for nothing.

00:59.482 --> 01:01.449
Why d'you think
they wear wellies - farmers?

01:01.450 --> 01:03.453
Forget the mud. It's to slot
the sheep's hind legs down

01:03.454 --> 01:05.441
'and keep 'em rigid...'
It is not!

01:05.441 --> 01:06.497
..while you're giving 'em one
up the bee-hind.

01:06.498 --> 01:08.473
Shut... up!

01:08.474 --> 01:11.437
Do you not know anything about the
countryside? Do you honestly think

01:11.438 --> 01:14.421
they'd waste time legislating against
it if it didn't really happen?

01:14.422 --> 01:16.437
I have to say, Mr Kershaw was

01:16.438 --> 01:19.493
unusually upset about being told one
of his sheep had been knocked down

01:19.494 --> 01:21.445
at side of road.
They always are!

01:21.446 --> 01:23.465
I'm telling you,
it's a very special relationship

01:23.466 --> 01:25.489
these farmers have
with their sheep.

01:25.490 --> 01:27.461
Draw your own conclusions.

01:27.462 --> 01:30.429
I suppose I'm attracted to Ollie
and he's a bit of a beast.

01:30.430 --> 01:33.429
'Well, there you go, you see.
I rest my case.'

01:33.430 --> 01:34.481
If you didn't want to see the funny
side,

01:34.482 --> 01:36.457
you shouldn't have joined
the police force...

01:36.458 --> 01:38.442
service... force.

01:48.438 --> 01:50.441
Oooh! Gotta go.

01:50.442 --> 01:53.405
Jenson Button's just streaked past
in a white tranny.

01:53.406 --> 01:55.926
'I think he's trying to smash
the land speed record, bless him.'

01:56.498 --> 01:59.449
And he's got a tail-light out.

01:59.450 --> 02:00.477
I think I might give him a tug.

02:00.478 --> 02:03.461
'OK, well, you be careful
and don't be long.'

02:03.462 --> 02:05.477
I wanna send everyone home
in ten minutes.

02:05.478 --> 02:07.474
I wanna go home in ten minutes.

